---
title: Herby Roast Chicken with tender broccoli and sweet chilli glaze
description: The star of this dish is succulent chicken coated in herbs and roasted until golden. Though this may be a classic when it comes to dinnertime ideas, the accompanying crispy wedges, tender broccoli, and sticky sauce ensure this recipe is anything but ordinary.
